==人權==
===分離主義===
{{main|東突厥斯坦獨立運動}}
新疆維吾爾族獨立運動主要發生在20世紀與21世紀初期，該運動支持者主張，應該由維吾爾人在新疆西南部的區域建立一個獨立的民族國家<ref>{{Cite web|title=Responses to Xinjiang ethnic unrest do not address underlying causes|url=https://www.scmp.com/comment/insight-opinion/article/1276012/responses-xinjiang-ethnic-unrest-do-not-address-underlying|access-date=2021-07-15|date=Invalid Date|work=South China Morning Post|language=en|archive-date=2021-10-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211016153441/https://www.scmp.com/comment/insight-opinion/article/1276012/responses-xinjiang-ethnic-unrest-do-not-address-underlying|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>[http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-06-27/deaths-from-clashes-in-china-s-xinjiang-area-rises-to-35.html Deaths From Clashes in China’s Xinjiang Area Rises to 35] {{Wayback|url=http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-06-27/deaths-from-clashes-in-china-s-xinjiang-area-rises-to-35.html|date=20141006195016}}. Bloomberg. Retrieved on 2013-07-12.</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title=The Uyghurs in Xinjiang – The Malaise Grows. After September 11th 2001, the Chinese regime strove to include its repression of Uyghur opposition within the international dynamic of the struggle against Islamic terrorist networks.|url=http://journals.openedition.org/chinaperspectives/648|last=Castets|first=Rémi|date=2003-10-01|journal=China Perspectives|issue=49|doi=10.4000/chinaperspectives.648|volume=2003|language=fr|issn=2070-3449|access-date=2021-07-15|archive-date=2021-12-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211208181812/https://journals.openedition.org/chinaperspectives/648|dead-url=no}}</ref>，因為作為他們祖國的[[東突厥斯坦|東突厥斯坦]]並非中國的一部分。對抗中國政府的分離恐怖主義活動被新疆眾多的地下激進組織所領導，其中[[東突厥斯坦伊斯蘭運動|東突厥斯坦伊斯蘭運動]]已被[[聯合國|聯合國]][[聯合國安全理事會|安理會]]和中國、英國等國認定為恐怖組織<ref>{{cite web|title=關於聯合國安理會制裁阿富汗委員會將 「東突厥斯坦伊斯蘭運動」列入 受制裁實體名單的通知|url=http://www.gov.cn/gongbao/content/2002/content_61790.htm|accessdate=2018-06-30|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180630185638/http://www.gov.cn/gongbao/content/2002/content_61790.htm|archivedate=2018-06-30|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/uk/2016/07/160720_uighur_uk_china_terror|title=英國將「東突」列入恐怖組織名單|date=2016-07-20|publisher=BBC中文網|accessdate=2018-06-30|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180719232647/https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/uk/2016/07/160720_uighur_uk_china_terror|archivedate=2018-07-19|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同時，美國長期資助「世維會」等「東突」組織；多名高官都曾出席與「東突」分裂勢力的會見、會議，為其站台。<ref>{{cite news|author=責任編輯： 劉陽|title=美國支持的「世維會」是不折不扣的恐怖主義代言人|url=http://www.xinhuanet.com/2019-12/06/c_1125318098.htm|accessdate=2021-04-17|agency=新華社|publisher=新華網|date=2019-12-06|archivedate=2021-04-21|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210421045630/http://www.xinhuanet.com/2019-12/06/c_1125318098.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>

===侵犯人權指控===
{{seealso|新疆恐怖活動列表|新疆再教育營|新疆種族滅絕指控}}
自[[2014年烏魯木齊火車南站暴力恐怖襲擊案件|2014年烏魯木齊火車南站暴力恐怖襲擊案件]]發生之後，在[[中國共產黨中央委員會總書記|中共中央總書記]][[習近平|習近平]]領導下<ref>{{cite news|title=紐約時報：中共文件顯示習近平主導新疆鎮壓|url=https://www.voachinese.com/a/nyt-leaked-documents-xinjiang-crackdown-xijinping-201911117/5169324.html|publisher=[[美國之音|美國之音]]中文|date=2019-11-17|accessdate=2019-11-27|archivedate=2019-11-17|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191117130336/https://www.voachinese.com/a/nyt-leaked-documents-xinjiang-crackdown-xijinping-201911117/5169324.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=USCC報告︰美國不應稱習近平「國家主席」 避免令人以為中國有民主|url=https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20191116/60273263|publisher=[[蘋果日報_(香港)|蘋果日報 (香港)]]|date=2019-11-16|accessdate=2019-11-27|archivedate=2019-11-16|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191116040051/https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20191116/60273263|dead-url=no}}</ref>，中華人民共和國政府首先在新疆發起「[[嚴厲打擊暴力恐怖活動專項行動|反恐人民戰爭]]」<ref>{{Cite journal|last1=Trédaniel|first1=Marie|last2=Lee|first2=Pak K.|date=2017-09-18|title=Explaining the Chinese framing of the "terrorist" violence in Xinjiang: insights from securitization theory|url=https://kar.kent.ac.uk/59699/1/Explaining%20the%20Chinese%20framing%20of%20the%20terrorist%20violence%20in%20Xinjiang%20insights%20from%20securitization%20theory_AM%20version.pdf|url-status=live|journal=Nationalities Papers|language=en|volume=46|issue=1|pages=177–195|doi=10.1080/00905992.2017.1351427|issn=0090-5992|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190427073133/https://kar.kent.ac.uk/59699/1/Explaining%20the%20Chinese%20framing%20of%20the%20terrorist%20violence%20in%20Xinjiang%20insights%20from%20securitization%20theory_AM%20version.pdf|archive-date=2019-04-27|access-date=2019-08-18|s2cid=157729459}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=2014：中国掀起“反恐人民战争”--时政--人民网|url=http://politics.people.com.cn/n/2014/1231/c1001-26309191.html|access-date=2022-01-17|work=politics.people.com.cn|archive-date=2022-05-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220517142009/http://politics.people.com.cn/n/2014/1231/c1001-26309191.html}}</ref>，並下令興建[[新疆再教育營|新疆職業技能教育培訓中心]]。2017年年初開始，多家中文、英文、阿拉伯文媒體報道稱[[新疆|新疆]]當局已投入100萬左右的人到再教育營進行封閉式國民教育和職業培訓<ref>{{cite web|title=新疆再教育營關人或近百萬 警察抓人有指標|url=https://www.voachinese.com/a/4383631.html|accessdate=2018-05-08|work=美國之音中文|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180508053017/https://www.voachinese.com/a/4383631.html|archivedate=2018-05-08|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=中國如何對少數民族進行「教育轉化」|url=https://cn.nytimes.com/opinion/20180516/china-re-education-camps/|accessdate=2018-05-16|work=www.cn.nytimes.com|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180516223911/https://cn.nytimes.com/opinion/20180516/china-re-education-camps/|archivedate=2018-05-16|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=美智庫: 新疆嚴控手段與德國納粹如出一轍|url=https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/shaoshuminzu/nu-07102018110927.html|accessdate=2018-07-10|work=www.cn.nytimes.com|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180711003404/https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/shaoshuminzu/nu-07102018110927.html|archivedate=2018-07-11|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=新疆「改造營」關押超百萬 強迫放棄信仰|url=http://www.chinaaid.net/2018/05/blog-post_46.html|accessdate=2018-05-29|work=chinaaid.net|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180728221754/http://www.chinaaid.net/2018/05/blog-post_46.html|archivedate=2018-07-28|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|author=الأربعاء 1 مايو|title=الصين: قصص مروعة لمسلمات من الإيغور خرجن من معسكرات الاعتقال|url=http://mubasher.aljazeera.net/news/%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%B5%D9%8A%D9%86-%D9%82%D8%B5%D8%B5-%D9%85%D8%B1%D9%88%D8%B9%D8%A9-%D9%84%D9%85%D8%B3%D9%84%D9%85%D8%A7%D8%AA-%D9%85%D9%86-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%A5%D9%8A%D8%BA%D9%88%D8%B1-%D8%AE%D8%B1%D8%AC%D9%86-%D9%85%D9%86-%D9%85%D8%B9%D8%B3%D9%83%D8%B1%D8%A7%D8%AA-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%A7%D8%B9%D8%AA%D9%82%D8%A7%D9%84|accessdate=2020-01-17|work=الجزيرة|agency=المصدر|archivedate=2020-11-16|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201116000520/http://mubasher.aljazeera.net/news/