根據[[路透社|路透社]]、[[美聯社|美聯社]]等媒體報道，自[[陳全國|陳全國]]就任中共新疆維吾爾自治區黨委書記以來，自治區當局在新疆進行了嚴厲的監控活動，包括設立「[[新疆再教育營|再教育營]]」<ref>{{Cite web|title=路透社偵查報道：新疆再教育營近39幢面積等如140個足球場|url=https://beta.thestandnews.com/china/%E8%B7%AF%E9%80%8F%E7%A4%BE%E5%81%B5%E6%9F%A5%E5%A0%B1%E9%81%93-%E6%96%B0%E7%96%86%E5%86%8D%E6%95%99%E8%82%B2%E7%87%9F%E8%BF%91-39-%E5%B9%A2-%E9%9D%A2%E7%A9%8D%E7%AD%89%E5%A6%82-140-%E5%80%8B%E8%B6%B3%E7%90%83%E5%A0%B4|accessdate=2021-05-26|date=2018-11-30|work=立場新聞|agency=路透社|language=zh-hk|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210527043024/https://beta.thestandnews.com/china/%E8%B7%AF%E9%80%8F%E7%A4%BE%E5%81%B5%E6%9F%A5%E5%A0%B1%E9%81%93-%E6%96%B0%E7%96%86%E5%86%8D%E6%95%99%E8%82%B2%E7%87%9F%E8%BF%91-39-%E5%B9%A2-%E9%9D%A2%E7%A9%8D%E7%AD%89%E5%A6%82-140-%E5%80%8B%E8%B6%B3%E7%90%83%E5%A0%B4|archivedate=2021-05-27|dead-url=no}}</ref>、強制安裝[[智能手機|智能手機]]內容掃描軟件<ref>{{Cite web|title=在新疆，你手機上不能有的73000項內容|url=https://cn.nytimes.com/technology/20190703/china-xinjiang-app/|accessdate=2021-05-25|date=2019-07-03|last=ZHONG|first=RAYMOND|work=紐約時報中文網|publisher=紐約時報|language=zh|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210617002215/https://cn.nytimes.com/technology/20190703/china-xinjiang-app/|archivedate=2021-06-17|dead-url=no}}</ref>、安排家庭[[結對認親|結對認親]]<ref>{{Cite web|title=監視從餐桌到床上：新疆實施「結對認親」，讓110萬中共幹部入住維吾爾家庭|url=https://www.thenewslens.com/article/110727|accessdate=2021-05-25|date=2018-12-23|last=Huang|first=Abby|work=關鍵評論|language=zh-tw|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210526003259/https://www.thenewslens.com/article/110727|archivedate=2021-05-26|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=「一家親」式監控滲入新疆|url=http://www.dw.com/zh/%E4%B8%80%E5%AE%B6%E4%BA%B2%E5%BC%8F%E7%9B%91%E6%8E%A7%E6%B8%97%E5%85%A5%E6%96%B0%E7%96%86/a-43794960?&zhongwen=simp|accessdate=2018-05-20|date=2018-05-18|language=zh|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180521022049/http://www.dw.com/zh/%E4%B8%80%E5%AE%B6%E4%BA%B2%E5%BC%8F%E7%9B%91%E6%8E%A7%E6%B8%97%E5%85%A5%E6%96%B0%E7%96%86/a-43794960?&zhongwen=simp|archivedate=2018-05-21|dead-url=no|publisher=德國之聲}}</ref>等等，特別是針對維吾爾族人。根據[[自由亞洲電台|自由亞洲電台]]和[[人權觀察|人權觀察]]的報告，僅在[[喀什地區|喀什地區]]就有超過12萬維吾爾族穆斯林被拘禁在此類再教育營內接受中國共產黨的政治教育。<ref>{{cite news|title=China 'holding at least 120,000 Uighurs in re-education camps'|url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2018/jan/25/at-least-120000-muslim-uighurs-held-in-chinese-re-education-camps-report|work=The Guardian|date=2018-01-25|accessdate=2018-08-18|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180819010931/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2018/jan/25/at-least-120000-muslim-uighurs-held-in-chinese-re-education-camps-report|archivedate=2018-08-19|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Former inmates of China’s Muslim ‘reeducation’ camps tell of brainwashing, torture|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/asia_pacific/former-inmates-of-chinas-muslim-re-education-camps-tell-of-brainwashing-torture/2018/05/16/32b330e8-5850-11e8-8b92-45fdd7aaef3c_story.html?utm_term=.a9cd3d95c511|accessdate=2018-08-18|date=2018-05-16|work=The Washington Post|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180922014930/https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/asia_pacific/former-inmates-of-chinas-muslim-re-education-camps-tell-of-brainwashing-torture/2018/05/16/32b330e8-5850-11e8-8b92-45fdd7aaef3c_story.html|archivedate=2018-09-22|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=China: Free Xinjiang ‘Political Education’ Detainees|url=https://www.hrw.org/news/2017/09/10/china-free-xinjiang-political-education-detainees|accessdate=2018-08-18|publisher=Human Rights Watch|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20181025174023/https://www.hrw.org/news/2017/09/10/china-free-xinjiang-political-education-detainees|archivedate=2018-10-25|dead-url=no}}</ref>一些人權組織和很多維吾爾族人批評這種政策加劇了新疆緊張的民族關係和反政府暴力活動。中國學術界的一些專家也擔心，封鎖整個地區、管控整個民族只會讓維吾爾族人產生積怨，而且陳的政策負擔沈重、費用高昂、難以為繼。新疆的漢族居民也抱怨生活在這樣一個警察國家的種種不便。<ref>{{cite news|author=蕭雨|title=新疆：一個露天監獄|url=https://www.voachinese.com/a/uyghur-freedom-china-20180228/4275386.html|accessdate=2018-03-03|work=美國之音|date=2018-03-02|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180303225134/https://www.voachinese.com/a/uyghur-freedom-china-20180228/4275386.html|archivedate=2018-03-03|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|author=米華健|title=新疆：天羅地網下的監控世界|url=https://cn.nytimes.com/opinion/20180205/china-surveillance-state-uighurs/|accessdate=2018-03-03|work=紐約時報中文網|date=2018-02-05|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180220091320/https://cn.nytimes.com/opinion/20180205/china-surveillance-state-uighurs/|archivedate=2018-02-20|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|author=JOSH CHIN|title=人權組織稱中國在新疆部署大數據警務預測平台|url=http://cn.wsj.com/gb/20180228/BCH115228.asp?utm_content=buffer94ae4&utm_medium=social&utm_source=twitter.com&utm_campaign=buffer|accessdate=2018-03-03|work=華爾街日報中文網|date=2018-02-28|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180303164749/http://cn.wsj.com/gb/20180228/BCH115228.asp?utm_content=buffer94ae4&utm_medium=social&utm_source=twitter.com&utm_campaign=buffer|archivedate=2018-03-03|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=新疆鐵腕控制 漢人也叫苦連天|url=http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/press-review-41999212|accessdate=2018-03-03|work=BBC中文網|date=2017-11-15|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180219162227/http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/press-review-41999212|archivedate=2018-02-19|dead-url=no}}</ref>中國政府則認為，這些舉措是依法採取的社會治理措施，旨在保障人民生命安全以及公民基本權利不受侵犯，幫助學員擺脫恐怖主義、宗教極端主義束縛，有利於新疆社會穩定和長治久安<ref>{{cite news|editor=劉瓊|title=新疆維吾爾自治區主席雪克來提·扎克爾就新疆反恐維穩情況及開展職業技能教育培訓工作答記者問|url=http://www.xinhuanet.com/politics/2018-10/16/c_1123564725.htm|accessdate=2021-05-27|agency=新華社|date=2018-10-16|archivedate=2021-05-27|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210527051339/http://www.xinhuanet.com/politics/2018-10/16/c_1123564725.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|editor=王禕|title=白皮書：教培中心保障學員基本權利不受侵犯|url=https://www.chinanews.com/gn/2019/08-16/8928647.shtml|accessdate=2021-05-27|agency=中新社|date=2019-08-16|archivedate=2021-05-27|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210527122404/https://www.chinanews.com/gn/2019/08-16/8928647.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在[[聯合國人權理事會|聯合國人權理事會]]第三十八次會議「新疆人權事業的發展與進步」主題邊會上，有中國學者表示中國政府的舉措是在「依法打擊和防範暴力恐怖活動」，並稱此舉有利於「維護國家安全、公共安全和人民生命財產安全，維護區域穩定，促進了相關國家的人權事業發展和進步」，一些國家政府、國際組織和非政府組織的代表及專家學者、媒體記者等共60余人參與會議，並表示他們對新疆人權事業發展的贊賞。<ref>{{cite web|title=看！這就是真實的新疆 ——中國人權研究會赴聯合國人權理事會第三十八次會議側記|url=http://world.people.com.cn/n1/2018/0630/c1002-30097097.html|accessdate=2018-06-30|publisher=人民網|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180630161953/http://world.people.com.cn/n1/2018/0630/c1002-30097097.html|archivedate=2018-06-30|dead-url=no}}</ref>

